1186
01:32:42,325 --> 01:32:45,128
Aku membunuhnya.
Ini sudah berakhir.

1187
01:32:45,163 --> 01:32:46,558
Kau gadis bodoh.

1188
01:32:46,593 --> 01:32:48,670
Itu hanya luka daging.

1189
01:32:48,705 --> 01:32:50,430
Jika dia sudah mati,

1190
01:32:50,465 --> 01:32:52,333
